name: agileproject
description: Construct a presurgical epilepsy evaluation system by pinpointing sources of brain activity using EEG data and rendering a 3D visualization of a brain. Build a user friendly application that will be convenient for surgeons to use and aid in their decision making.
author: Rohan Balani, Daniel Partika, Kyle Boberg, Charles Canata, Susan McAloon, Daniel Kang
